{"id": "1443893379858698341", "channel_id": "1443394213344444446", "type": 19, "author_id": "262766198272294913", "author_name": "quaso177013", "author_bot": false, "content": "Noted, thanks for the help", "timestamp": "2025-11-28T09:16:48+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["248551659771265026"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1443626304099319859", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1443394213344444446", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Teambuilding Poison for Astral Reign", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1443893632229838898", "channel_id": "1443394213344444446", "type": 0, "author_id": "262766198272294913", "author_name": "quaso177013", "author_bot": false, "content": "Outside this event though, what should I try to invest in to get a decent Poison team long term?", "timestamp": "2025-11-28T09:17:48.170000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1443394213344444446", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Teambuilding Poison for Astral Reign", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1443951090386337844", "channel_id": "1443394213344444446", "type": 19, "author_id": "248551659771265026", "author_name": "unicorned_batman", "author_bot": false, "content": "There's 2 main poison teams for endgame:\n24 - Miryam - GDoll - Flex\nNymph - GDoll - Agrippa - Flex\nThe first functions by dealing damage and applying poison through it, while the second stalls to hell and back while applying poison through skills.\nThe first is easier to play in my opinion but tends to be a bit squishy, while the other one requires you to know mechanics and takes ages to clear since you're stalling a lot.\n\nI wouldn't solely focus on a poison team though, since a lot of bosses down the line have the ability to clear the poison off of themselves.", "timestamp": "2025-11-28T13:06:07.262000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["262766198272294913"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🫡", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1443893379858698341", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1443394213344444446", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Teambuilding Poison for Astral Reign", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
